{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"f6256c5052","title":"宁可丧失一些地方不可勉强作战","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"e95494b8c8","index":0,"year":1946,"month":7,"day":30,"articleId":"f6256c5052"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji21","name":"毛泽东全集第21卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji21.pdf"},{"id":"wenji4","name":"毛泽东文集第四卷（1999）","internal":false,"official":true,"type":"pdf","author":"中央文献研究室","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives9/main/books/wenji4.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji21":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"06a69e601c","type":"paragraph","text":"宁可丧失一些地方不可勉强作战","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji21","articleId":"f6256c5052"},{"id":"4160c0addd","type":"paragraph","text":"（1946年7月30日）张、邓、要”在我军主力未获充分补充休息恢复疲劳以前，及敌未进至有利于我之地形条件以前，宁可丧失一些地方，不可举行勉强的无把握的作战。此次菜部歼敌二方中，打得很好，今后作战亦不要过于性急，总以打胜使为原则。敌以十方大军尚我进攻，我损失若干地方是不可免的。你们应有对付恶务环境之精神与组织准备","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji21","articleId":"f6256c5052"},{"id":"0210c9787e","type":"paragraph","text":"军委","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji21","articleId":"f6256c5052"},{"id":"838592fd25","type":"paragraph","text":"中三十[1]张，指张鼎悉（1898-1981），福建永定人，当时任华中军区司令员。邓，指邓子恢（1896--1972），福建党岩人，当时任华中军区政治委员。票，指要裕，当时任华中军区副司令员。[2]指华中野战军1946年7月进行的宜家堡、泰兴战斗和如（桌）南龄","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji21","articleId":"f6256c5052"}],"page":{"id":"e57ddacccb","publicationId":"maoquanji21","articleId":"f6256c5052","start":539,"end":539}},"wenji4":{"comments":[{"id":"38db8130d8","publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"f6256c5052","index":-1,"part_index":-1,"offset":-1,"text":"根据毛泽东手稿刊印。"},{"id":"b2da33a6c9","publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"f6256c5052","index":2,"part_index":2,"offset":68,"text":"指华中野战军一九四六年七月进行的宣家堡、泰兴战斗和如（皋）南战斗，两次战斗共歼灭国民党军一万三千余人。"},{"id":"d51431a00e","publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"f6256c5052","index":1,"part_index":1,"offset":5,"text":"张，指张鼎丞（一八九八——一九八一），福建永定人，当时任华中军区司令员。邓，指邓子恢（一八九六——一九七二），福建龙岩人，当时任华中军区政治委员。粟，指粟裕，当时任华中军区副司令员。"}],"contents":[{"id":"084f2e4d95","type":"paragraph","text":"午三十","index":4,"publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"f6256c5052"},{"id":"0e1c7232a1","type":"title","text":"宁可丧失一些地方不可勉强作战","index":0,"publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"f6256c5052"},{"id":"3c986f2639","type":"paragraph","text":"军 委","index":3,"publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"f6256c5052"},{"id":"b2da33a6c9","type":"paragraph","text":"在我军主力未获充分补充休息恢复疲劳以前，及敌未进至有利于我之地形条件以前，宁可丧失一些地方，不可举行勉强的无把握的作战。此次粟部歼敌二万，打得很好，今后作战亦不要过于性急，总以打胜仗为原则。敌以十万大军向我进攻，我损失若干地方是不可免的。你们应有对付恶劣环境之精神与组织准备。","index":2,"publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"f6256c5052"},{"id":"d51431a00e","type":"appellation","text":"张、邓、粟：","index":1,"publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"f6256c5052"}],"page":{"id":"7f3b3b0b5c","publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"f6256c5052","start":181,"end":181}}}},"__N_SSG":true}